OL,3,C'Golden Boy' surgeon can return to
OL,4,Cwork following harassment suspension
OL,6,FA surgeon found to have sexually
OL,7,Fharassed and made racist comments to a
OL,8,Fnumber of colleagues will be free to
OL,9,Freturn to practising this month
OL,10,Ffollowing a tribunal.
OL,12,FJames Gilbert was a senior registrar
OL,13,Fin 2008 and 2009 for Oxford University
OL,14,FHospitals (OUH) NHS Trust and worked
OL,15,Fas a consultant between 2010 and 2022.
OL,17,FDescribed as the 'golden boy' for
OL,18,Ftransplants in Oxford, he was given an
OL,19,F8 month suspension for misconduct
OL,20,Fwhich was extended to 12 months
OL,21,Ffollowing a High Court ruling.
