OL,3,C'Golden Boy' surgeon can return to
OL,4,Cwork following harassment suspension
OL,6,FThe Medical Practitioners Tribunal
OL,7,FService (MPTS) found Mr Gilbert was
OL,8,F"remorseful" and the General Medical
OL,9,FCouncil (GMC), which had argued in the
OL,10,Fpast he should be struck off the
OL,11,Fmedical register, said it
OL,12,F"acknowledged" the findings.
OL,14,FMr Gilbert told the hearing he wanted
OL,15,Fto be an "ambassador for change in
OL,16,Fchallenging power imbalances between
OL,17,Fsenior and junior colleagues".
