OL,3,C'Golden Boy' surgeon can return to
OL,4,Cwork following harassment suspension
OL,6,FHe told the tribunal that he had taken
OL,7,Fcourses on professional boundaries,
OL,8,Funconscious bias and introduced a 'no
OL,9,Ftouch' policy saying he had gone
OL,10,Fthrough a "fundamental rethinking."
OL,12,FGilbert recalled how he was deeply
OL,13,Fsorry to the victims and was "deeply
OL,14,Fashamed of the person I once was." He
OL,15,Fsaid he is "determined not to repeat
OL,16,Fpast actions."
