OL,3,C'Golden Boy' surgeon can return to
OL,4,Cwork following harassment suspension
OL,6,FThe previous tribunal found the doctor
OL,7,Fhad targeted a junior female colleague
OL,8,Fby massaging her shoulders without
OL,9,Fconsent multiple times and squeezing
OL,10,Fher thighs under the operating table.
OL,12,FIn other claims he told the woman:
OL,13,F"You're a well together girl, you must
OL,14,Falways wear matching underwear. What
OL,15,Fkind are you wearing now?"
OL,17,FThe High Court judgement also found
OL,18,FGilbert imitated an Indian accent,
OL,19,Ftelling a man "when are you leaving
OL,20,Fthe country now?" in reference to
OL,21,FBrexit.
